column5: Happy first day of spring everybody!!
nice gator bud. were you lookin around in the vid to make sure nobody was watching when you pulled it up? hahaha
Wow, great vid. Nice camera position and angle with respect to the sun, and nice pike as well thats a sweet size.
Beautiful fish.  I'd love to get up there once more before the ice is gone.

Great report and video trophypikehunter  The ice where you shot this vid looks the same as the local lake my daughter and I were today.  Still a good 16" of ice left.  Beautiful gator!!! Good job and congratulations  Thanks for sharing Leechman
